_sText:
Haven't been too many maps being created as of late, so I decided to make one. As the title suggests, it takes place in a dark forest (though don't worry, the map isn't too dark to see anything!)

Map contains 25 pushable traps, 2 non-pushable traps, and 2 secret nades. 49 CT Spawns, 2 T spawns.

Made for steamgamers.com deathrun, 66.150.121.71:27015.
